<specimenCount box="[1268,1435,1310,1333]" pageId="20" pageNumber="687" type="generic">two specimens</specimenCount>
collected in Cantareira on 
<date box="[1123,1313,1342,1365]" pageId="20" pageNumber="687" value="1939-10-29">29 October 1939</date>
; Sඍൺංඇൾඌ +| Gൺඋർටൺ-Rඈൻඅൾൽඈ (2014) published the same specimens again and added some additional ones collected on different dates. The occurrence in 
<collectingCountry box="[1216,1306,1438,1461]" name="Ecuador" pageId="20" pageNumber="687">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
(Sඍൺංඇൾඌ +| Gൺඋർටൺ-Rඈൻඅൾൽඈ 2014) is dubious and probably based on misidentification, and thus it is removed from the species range.
</paragraph>
